332
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:15,839
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, sola skriptura je nešto

333
00:22:15,839 --> 00:22:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] što je temelj za svaku protestansku zajednicu,

334
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] svaku protestansku crkvu,

335
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga samo jedino i sljučivo i sveto pismo.

336
00:22:23,539 --> 00:22:25,180
[SPEAKER_00] E, ali tu imamo jedan problem.

337
00:22:25,180 --> 00:22:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] Već je Martin Luther, vrlo lukavo,

338
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,779
[SPEAKER_00] one dijelove svetoga pisma

339
00:22:28,779 --> 00:22:31,079
[SPEAKER_00] koje mu nisu što imali izbacio iz kanona,

340
00:22:31,079 --> 00:22:34,700
[SPEAKER_00] pa tako, mi kada govorimo o svetome pismu

341
00:22:34,700 --> 00:22:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] kao u knjizi koja je bitna,

342
00:22:36,460 --> 00:22:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] objavljena Božja riječ za svakoga kršćanina,

343
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:42,259
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga, imamo razliku,

344
00:22:42,259 --> 00:22:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] razliku u tim knjigama,

345
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, u kanonu,

346
00:22:44,880 --> 00:22:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] to je zbir knjiga koji su sadržani

347
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] u svetom pismu staroga i novoga zavijeta,

348
00:22:50,059 --> 00:22:51,339
[SPEAKER_00] imamo razliku.

349
00:22:51,339 --> 00:22:52,779
[SPEAKER_00] Postoje razlike

350
00:22:52,779 --> 00:22:54,819
[SPEAKER_00] i nije rijetkost da se u određenim

351
00:22:54,819 --> 00:22:56,160
[SPEAKER_00] protestanskim izdanjima,

352
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:58,579
[SPEAKER_00] čak i dijelovi iz evanđelja ili citati,

353
00:22:58,579 --> 00:23:01,240
[SPEAKER_00] koji ne odgovaraju, jednostavno izostave.

354
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:03,339
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je isto ovoga bitno.

355
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:06,400
[SPEAKER_00] i tu, recimo, posebna napomena

356
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] za katolike,

357
00:23:07,420 --> 00:23:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] za nas koji se trudimo živjeti u svoje vjeri,

358
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

359
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] nama je također sveto pismo

360
00:23:14,119 --> 00:23:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] sveta knjiga,

361
00:23:15,059 --> 00:23:16,839
[SPEAKER_00] jednako kao i protestantima.

362
00:23:16,839 --> 00:23:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je nešto što nas bližava,

363
00:23:18,980 --> 00:23:19,799
[SPEAKER_00] to ćemo vidjeti kasnije,

364
00:23:19,799 --> 00:23:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] da je to i dodirna točka

365
00:23:21,579 --> 00:23:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] između protestanskih crkava

366
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:25,299
[SPEAKER_00] i katoličke crkve.

367
00:23:25,299 --> 00:23:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ali moramo tu biti jasni.

368
00:23:27,140 --> 00:23:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ponovno to učiteljstvo,

369
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] ponovno ta tradicija katoličke crkve

370
00:23:31,599 --> 00:23:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] odredila taj zbir svijetih knjiga

371
00:23:34,420 --> 00:23:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] koje sadržavaju sveto pismo.

372
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] A ovdje nismo pozvani izbacivati

373
00:23:39,559 --> 00:23:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] ili nismo pozvani tumačiti

374
00:23:41,519 --> 00:23:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] ili reći samo ono što ti štima,

375
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] nego sveto pismo gledati u cijelini

376
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] kao Bogom nadaknutu riječ Božju

377
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] koja je tu radi tebe i radi mene

378
00:23:50,019 --> 00:23:53,259
[SPEAKER_00] da nas promijeni, da nas učini boljim ljudima.

379
00:23:53,259 --> 00:23:55,700
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko o temi Svetoga pisma.

380
00:23:55,700 --> 00:23:57,700
[SPEAKER_00] Čistilište.

381
00:23:57,700 --> 00:24:01,240
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte, bilo kojem protestantu za čistilište

382
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] počeva će vam se smijeti.

383
00:24:02,519 --> 00:24:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne postoji u protestanskim zajednicama,

384
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] crkvama pojam čistilišta kao takav.

385
00:24:08,839 --> 00:24:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas da, kod katolika da.

386
00:24:10,980 --> 00:24:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] U protestanskim crkvama ne.

387
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:16,619
[SPEAKER_00] Htio sam samo to istaknuti radi jasnoće.

388
00:24:16,619 --> 00:24:20,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tema spasenja, vrlo kompleksna.

389
00:24:20,220 --> 00:24:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pokušat ću to najjednostavnije.

390
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:26,759
[SPEAKER_00] To bi u teologiji rekli onak malo preciznije.

391
00:24:26,759 --> 00:24:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] To su dogmatske sad nekakve razlike.

392
00:24:28,880 --> 00:24:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] I sad je to onako komplicirano.

393
00:24:31,579 --> 00:24:34,259
[SPEAKER_00] Malo sam to razmišljao kako to što pojednostavljenije

394
00:24:34,259 --> 00:24:35,759
[SPEAKER_00] reći, izreći.

395
00:24:35,759 --> 00:24:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] I domislio sam, pa evo nadam se

396
00:24:38,220 --> 00:24:39,099
[SPEAKER_00] da ćete me razumijeti.

397
00:24:39,099 --> 00:24:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kada govorimo o temi spasenja,

398
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] cilj moga, tvoga, našega života je,

399
00:24:46,799 --> 00:24:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] Stjepan je o tome govorio,

400
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:50,259
[SPEAKER_00] to kraljestvo nebesko u propovijedi.

401
00:24:50,259 --> 00:24:52,700
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, na kraju krajeva i doći u nebo.

402
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:55,799
[SPEAKER_00] Biti u zajedništvu sa svojim Bogom.

403
00:24:55,799 --> 00:24:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ostvariti spasenje svoje vlastite duše,

404
00:24:58,859 --> 00:25:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] svoga tijela na kraju krajeva,

405
00:25:00,480 --> 00:25:02,359
[SPEAKER_00] koji će uskrsnuti u posljednji dan.

406
00:25:02,359 --> 00:25:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] I kako se postiže to spasenje?

407
00:25:07,099 --> 00:25:07,660
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavnije.

408
00:25:07,660 --> 00:25:10,640
[SPEAKER_00] Mi, katolici,

409
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,839
[SPEAKER_00] ono, nisam sada provjerio nauku,

410
00:25:12,839 --> 00:25:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] ono, kak će posti spasenje.

411
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:15,819
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, potrebna ti je vjera

412
00:25:15,819 --> 00:25:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] u Isusa Hrista,

413
00:25:17,559 --> 00:25:19,140
[SPEAKER_00] potrebna je milost Božja,

414
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali potrebna su i dobra dijela.

415
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] Potrebno je i ono što ti činiš.

416
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:26,259
[SPEAKER_00] Potrebno je,

417
00:25:26,259 --> 00:25:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] potreban je tvoj vlastiti angažman.

418
00:25:29,440 --> 00:25:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] u protestantskim crkvama,

419
00:25:30,940 --> 00:25:31,740
[SPEAKER_00] zajednicama,

420
00:25:31,740 --> 00:25:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljno je ljudi vjera.

421
00:25:33,559 --> 00:25:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tako oni uče,

422
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] tako oni doživljava.

423
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je zbog toga,

424
00:25:37,579 --> 00:25:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] iz tog razloga,

425
00:25:38,619 --> 00:25:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] nema nauka u čistilištu

426
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:41,660
[SPEAKER_00] i smiju nam se zbog toga.

427
00:25:41,660 --> 00:25:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jer,

428
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] ako si jedan put povjerovao u gospodina,

429
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] to je to.

430
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si spašen.

431
00:25:46,579 --> 00:25:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš živjeti životom kakvim god hoćeš

432
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] i ništa ti se neće dogoditi.

433
00:25:50,799 --> 00:25:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ti si spašen.

434
00:25:52,380 --> 00:25:53,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ti vjeruješ

435
00:25:53,299 --> 00:25:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] i to ti je dovoljno.

436
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tu sad već vidite,

437
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,859
[SPEAKER_00] kao dobro odgojeni katolici,

438
00:25:57,859 --> 00:25:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] zabludu.

439
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:00,839
[SPEAKER_00] Zabludu.

440
00:26:00,839 --> 00:26:04,160
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to nije u skladu sa Svetim pismom.

441
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:06,299
[SPEAKER_00] Jer što će ti vjera bez dijela?

442
00:26:06,299 --> 00:26:07,240
[SPEAKER_00] Takva vjera je mrtva.

443
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:08,759
[SPEAKER_00] Čini mi se da piše negdje.

444
00:26:08,759 --> 00:26:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ovoga u Svetome pismu pišeš.

445
00:26:11,039 --> 00:26:11,700
[SPEAKER_00] Žalim se.

446
00:26:11,700 --> 00:26:12,819
[SPEAKER_00] 100%.

447
00:26:12,819 --> 00:26:13,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ovoga.

448
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:14,259
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

449
00:26:14,259 --> 00:26:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] jednako su važna

450
00:26:15,599 --> 00:26:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] i milost Božja

451
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] i vjera.

452
00:26:18,559 --> 00:26:19,740
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, naš čin vjere,

453
00:26:19,740 --> 00:26:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali jednako i naš vlastiti angažman.

454
00:26:22,579 --> 00:26:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

455
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] to je po pitanju spasenja,

456
00:26:24,779 --> 00:26:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] a s druge strane,

457
00:26:26,019 --> 00:26:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] kada govorim o protestantskim crkvama,

458
00:26:29,539 --> 00:26:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljna je samo vjera.

459
00:26:31,180 --> 00:26:32,240
[SPEAKER_00] Sola, Fidej,

460
00:26:32,240 --> 00:26:32,900
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga,

461
00:26:32,900 --> 00:26:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] taj njihov čuveni treći,

462
00:26:34,599 --> 00:26:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] još jedan od samo Sola.

463
00:26:36,420 --> 00:26:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo sljedeći slajd.

464
00:26:38,099 --> 00:26:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

465
00:26:40,619 --> 00:26:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] stavio sam određene razlike.

466
00:26:43,779 --> 00:26:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] Određene razlike,

467
00:26:45,119 --> 00:26:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da sam bio jasan,

468
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] neću se ovdje ponavljati,

469
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] otišao sam malo dalje,

470
00:26:50,119 --> 00:26:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] idemo vidjeti ipak

471
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] koje su to i dodirne točke.

472
00:26:52,900 --> 00:26:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

473
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što nas upravo naša

474
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:55,660
[SPEAKER_00] sveta,

475
00:26:55,660 --> 00:26:56,099
[SPEAKER_00] rimska,

476
00:26:56,099 --> 00:26:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] katolička crkva

477
00:26:57,180 --> 00:26:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] uči

478
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] da trebamo imati

479
00:26:59,220 --> 00:26:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] taj

480
00:26:59,599 --> 00:27:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] raspoloživi duh.

481
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:04,259
[SPEAKER_00] to je baština nauka,

482
00:27:04,259 --> 00:27:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] učiteljstva katoličke crkve,

483
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] kada govorim o tome,

484
00:27:07,319 --> 00:27:08,299
[SPEAKER_00] a to je tema

485
00:27:08,299 --> 00:27:09,339
[SPEAKER_00] ekumenizma,

486
00:27:09,339 --> 00:27:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] zbližavanja,

487
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:12,359
[SPEAKER_00] zbližavanja

488
00:27:12,359 --> 00:27:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] među svim kršćanskim crkvama,

489
00:27:14,019 --> 00:27:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] vjerni,

490
00:27:15,059 --> 00:27:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] opet Kristovoj riječi,

491
00:27:16,319 --> 00:27:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] da svi budemo jedni,

492
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:19,319
[SPEAKER_00] ujedinjeni u molitvi,

493
00:27:19,319 --> 00:27:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] da svi budemo jedni,

494
00:27:21,039 --> 00:27:22,640
[SPEAKER_00] da svi budemo jedno,

495
00:27:23,119 --> 00:27:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] onako kako je kriz želio

496
00:27:24,420 --> 00:27:25,180
[SPEAKER_00] i kako je molio

497
00:27:25,180 --> 00:27:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] i kako je zapisano

498
00:27:26,420 --> 00:27:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] u Ivanovom evanđelju.

499
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:29,299
[SPEAKER_00] I na tome tragu

500
00:27:29,299 --> 00:27:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] ekumenizma,

501
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] kada govorimo o razlici sakramenata,

502
00:27:32,519 --> 00:27:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] spomenuo sam određene razlike

503
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] koje postoje,

504
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] imamo jednu veliku sličnost,

505
00:27:37,460 --> 00:27:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] to je krštenje.

506
00:27:38,180 --> 00:27:40,220
[SPEAKER_00] To je recimo jedna dodirna točka

507
00:27:40,220 --> 00:27:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] krštenje

508
00:27:41,039 --> 00:27:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] koje je takvo

509
00:27:42,180 --> 00:27:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] i koje je priznato

510
00:27:43,480 --> 00:27:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] i koje oni priznaju,

511
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,359
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

512
00:27:45,359 --> 00:27:46,680
[SPEAKER_00] da je jedan čin

513
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] po kojem mi postajemo

514
00:27:48,420 --> 00:27:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] ljubljena djeca Božja,

515
00:27:49,819 --> 00:27:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] to je recimo jedna dodirna točka

516
00:27:51,779 --> 00:27:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] između svih protestanskih crkava

517
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] i katoličke crkve.

518
00:27:55,539 --> 00:27:58,359
[SPEAKER_00] Zatim,

519
00:27:58,359 --> 00:28:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] osoba Isusa Hrista,

520
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:00,799
[SPEAKER_00] evidentno,

521
00:28:00,799 --> 00:28:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

522
00:28:01,119 --> 00:28:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujemo jednoga Boga,

523
00:28:02,380 --> 00:28:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

524
00:28:03,539 --> 00:28:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujemo Isusa Hrista

525
00:28:05,059 --> 00:28:06,660
[SPEAKER_00] u njegovu smrtu,

526
00:28:06,660 --> 00:28:07,700
[SPEAKER_00] njegovu skrsnuće,

527
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] samo postoje tu

528
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] različite interpretacije,

529
00:28:10,619 --> 00:28:12,359
[SPEAKER_00] ali osoba Isusa Hrista

530
00:28:12,359 --> 00:28:12,779
[SPEAKER_00] je ta

531
00:28:12,779 --> 00:28:14,200
[SPEAKER_00] koja nas spaja.

532
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,319
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao sam

533
00:28:15,319 --> 00:28:17,200
[SPEAKER_00] tijekom izlaganja,

534
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,819
[SPEAKER_00] nikada nemoj,

535
00:28:18,819 --> 00:28:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] dragi brate i sestro,

536
00:28:20,519 --> 00:28:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] imati

537
00:28:21,099 --> 00:28:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] isključivi stav

538
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:23,339
[SPEAKER_00] prema nekoga

539
00:28:23,339 --> 00:28:24,279
